This is the overall structure of a research project related to the BCI and DL courses.
The presentation is in Google drive in Word, ... in Cloud.
The paper is being developed and saved in Overleaf in LaTex in Cloud using both overleaf and sharedLaTex.
The code/ impl/ misc/ data are all being developed in GitHub Cloud after expriencing hg-Mercurial and svn-Subversion repositories.
The code is being developed in Python/ openSourced, using Anaconda for virtual env creation, and ipynb using ipython kernel IDE/ interactive python.